  "name": "Morrison COU2 \u2014 VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Accepted, W-CON-01)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors have been reviewed; 12 carry structured requiredLevel and achievedLevel scores. The model form factor was evaluated through an extended qualitative assessment process and is documented narratively; the assessment team concluded that the overall evidence base supports acceptance. Decision: Accepted.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
